# Next.js server package

- Small **Next.js 15** App Router app under `server/src/app/`.
- Today: `GET /api/health` for deploy verification.
- Do not add Supabase **service role** keys until there is a real server-side use case; never expose service role to the client.

## Conventions
- API routes: `server/src/app/api/<name>/route.ts`.
- Keep handlers thin; validate inputs if accepting POST bodies.
